Hi Marcel, 
the neighborlist is used in preprocessing and calculates the indices. Since we compute the actual distance within autograd, it should still work.

@Stefaanhess uses stress in the dev branch and it seems to work. Unfortunately, it is not documented yet:
You have to apply `schnetpack.atomistic.Strain` to the input before passing it into the representation and differentiate w.r.t to `properties.strain`.

@Stefaanhess Maybe you could add an example for this to the new modelzoo with @NiklasGebauer?
